{"tid":312814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"街頭胸襲日女兼打人 中國男東京被捕","createTime":"2017-07-07T18:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T00:31:24.000Z","uid":92301,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12ae9c77c141e71d962ff64b4d551e7b2c57598f","tid":312814,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7fl4yrj5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7fl4yrj5&h=b9f35924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京一名28歲中國男子，涉嫌今年5月在街頭非禮女性，更動粗打傷事主。疑犯周五（7日）被警方拘捕，他回答警方問話時，聲稱「因為見那女子漂亮，就想摸她。」 <br />\n<br />\n警方指，被捕的鄭勇男報稱兼職維生，他今年5月在東京大田區街頭，向一名跑步回家途中20餘歲日本女子上下其手，先摸臀繼而胸襲。女子大聲呼救，鄭竟動粗踢向女子背部數次，令女子受傷，預計需治療一個月。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170707/mobile/bknint-20170707153406478-0707_17011_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170707%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170707153406478-0707_17011_001.html%23popupGallery&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6Cf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=077fb43e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170707/mobile/bknint-20170707153406478-0707_17011_001.html#popupGallery</a>"},{"pid":"676967ab06b7a9ad1cfb00653dad895ff32d3897","tid":312814,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8e9c15eaaaa74ed64a0b99e8c069eee3c47a7a","tid":312814,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"都唔似廿八才"},{"pid":"61e05a077d674910bd40ac0e8e0d17f188dac9c2","tid":312814,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:51:34.000Z","msg":"支那豬有樣睇"},{"pid":"277ec15a1e34f162b1db848ae830a57efce8e208","tid":312814,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那豬有樣睇</blockquote><br />\n第一眼望去我以為係相撲手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad